            "title": "盤中速報 - 今國光(6209)股價拉至漲停，漲停價65.3元，成交12,609張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>今國光(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6209:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6209\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6209-TW</a>)12日09:14上漲5.9元，股價漲停報65.3元，委買9,895張，成交12,609張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為光學鏡片、光學鏡頭之製造。光學鏡片、光學鏡頭之買賣。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>今國光(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6209:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6209\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6209-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲4.21%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲0.82%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-665 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-711 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+46 張</li> <li>融資增減：+637 張</li> <li>融券增減：+337 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
